This project was kludged together from these projects:

- https://github.com/silverfix/python-ircd
- https://github.com/gaston770/python-chord

current features:

- local irc server as user interface
- channels are hosted by DHT nodes

needs python 2.7 and twisted


current usage:


'''
python main.py -D 8000 -P 6667 -remote None
'''
sets up a server with port 8000 as the dht port and 6667 as the local irc server

'''
python main.py -D 8000 -P 6667 -remote otherip:port
'''

creates a server and connects it to otherip:port
